detail.name: Overwhelming Confidence
detail.effect: [Activate Main] Place the top 3 cards of your deck into their owner's Drop : Draw 1 card. Then, play up to 1 Battle Card with a cost of 4 or less and 《Saiyan》 in its special traits from your Drop.

detail.name: 圧倒的な自信
detail.effect: 【起動 メイン】自分のデッキの上から3枚をドロップに置く：カード1枚を引く。その後、自分のドロップからコスト4以下の特徴《サイヤ人》を持つバトルカード1枚までを登場させる。

faq.question: Can you activate this card's [Activate Main] skill if you have 2 or fewer cards in your deck?
